lead_paragraph: Formula One world champion Lewis Hamilton struggled to describe his feelings after the body blow of an engine failure in Russian Grand Prix qualifying on Saturday, but 'numb' did not cover it.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton Seeks Traces of Light on Another Dark Day
